text: The Military of Fascist Italy was the armed forces of the Fascist Italy, During the Interwar period and World War II. List of military and paramilitary forces: * Royal Italian Army (Regio Esercito - RE) * Blackshirts (MVSN - Voluntary Militia for National Security) were paramilitary wings of National Fascist Party (PNF) Category:1943 establishments in Europe Category:1945 disestablishments in Europe
title: Military of Fascist Italy
